# Interact with / Collect Objects and Unlock an Objective Marker
Design Brief and Tech Spec 

##Intention
Give the player a goal to reach.
Force the player to traverse the level by interacting with or collecting objects to unlock the goal.
Giving the player a visual indicator to move towards.

##Technical Spec
Visually represented Items
Buttons
Different colours
Visually represented Goal
Door
Shows what coloured buttons you need to press

On reaching items, interact or collect it
Notify some other system that it has been reached
